{"title":"MUE_Abstinencia_OH","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/MUE - Medicina de Urgencia/MUE_Abstinencia_OH.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Abstinencia OH\\Nen la Persona Mayor\\N(MUE)","guid":"02DcMrJcSN2q_VzdRKCIRg","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Definiciones y Contexto","guid":"LtJ6AclMS3STzlODyF-FsA","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"AUD (DSM-5) → patrón desadaptativo ≥2 criterios/12m","guid":"tgixKyouT3iPz4xjE9pJeA","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"AM → criterios pierden sensibilidad (tolerancia ~, jubilación, aislamiento)","guid":"tFKT_x59QdKETbJ2bJyEcA","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"2","text":"Prevalencia AUD en ≥65a ~ 8-10% (subestimada)","guid":"-ZE1i4r4ST-ABSSUc6fYNg","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"2","text":"\"Hidden drinking\" → consumo oculto, normalizado por la familia","guid":"Vho0sMQEQVaMbzbcZDLAjA","children":[]}]},{"id":"6","parent":"1","text":"AWS (Alcohol Withdrawal Syndrome)","guid":"JTqrgmnUQIiSBysCWM6b2g","children":[{"id":"7","parent":"6","text":"Espectro: leve → convulsiones → alucinosis → DT","guid":"4UcB3N4aRuS_2lSlQOB25g","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"6","text":"Afecta al 50% de AUD al cesar consumo","guid":"3TCkX0kESD23noBRpCWcaA","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"6","text":"En AM → mayor morbimortalidad, duración prolongada, atipia","guid":"sOnWh9ZMR1eJhwUn6iVp8Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"10","parent":"1","text":"Factores de riesgo ESPECÍFICOS en AM","guid":"7ZxpoHzRTbuTqJwG9sJINw","children":[{"id":"11","parent":"10","text":"Viudez reciente / duelo","guid":"2262vj0jSj--xZQDfixaOA","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"10","text":"Institucionalización","guid":"DS9pcQI4SEW0OQJHgQHG_Q","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"10","text":"Dolor crónico no tratado","guid":"WDQJIM66Q6ufipX7mBm2yw","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"10","text":"Trastornos del sueño","guid":"GP9FCGWRSJKaPp0dMprGug","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"10","text":"Comorbilidad psiquiátrica (depresión)","guid":"VazyrlXJTrus6KB_mO-JMQ","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"10","text":"Polifarmacia sedante","guid":"BZweaYL7TX-c_3c8lEkYIw","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"10","text":"AUD de inicio tardío (\"late onset\") ~ 1/3 de casos","guid":"8JFaMsQOSsOb-75OhSW-Tg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"18","parent":"0","text":"Fisiopatología","guid":"AXa8NCCaSSygx4X8Zk91XQ","children":[{"id":"19","parent":"18","text":"Consumo crónico de OH","guid":"WYX1LLk-QcqQwJHsdVgSQA","children":[{"id":"20","parent":"19","text":"↑ tono GABAérgico (receptor GABA-A)","guid":"TZF0eQQmS9KxoFwAzh_Bjg","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"19","text":"↓ regulación de receptores GABA","guid":"xLO96qUuQn67oFsDL0cbSA","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"19","text":"↑ regulación receptores NMDA (glutamato)","guid":"-b0rh3Q7RjWk1LL-FxE_vg","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"19","text":"Adaptación homeostática del SNC","guid":"CQGTfvhvT0GvCRN2g_kmyg","children":[]}]},{"id":"24","parent":"18","text":"Cese abrupto","guid":"2MJqqWxIS9io-fwtrU5Ykw","children":[{"id":"25","parent":"24","text":"Pérdida de inhibición GABA → hiperexcitabilidad","guid":"UIQTTwOlSpamKc7fJJ1g4A","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"24","text":"Sobreactivación NMDA → excitotoxicidad, convulsiones","guid":"mOjjbTe4SL6gMyr3s6MqzQ","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"24","text":"↑ Noradrenalina central (locus coeruleus) → síntomas autonómicos","guid":"lygdfjj2TdmpHZQ7gj6FFA","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"24","text":"↑ Dopamina → alucinaciones, agitación","guid":"qpeujZszRB-OjC-E9uI8xw","children":[]}]},{"id":"29","parent":"18","text":"Efecto KINDLING","guid":"WXdp7WMZS8CnWHJDM91ERA","children":[{"id":"30","parent":"29","text":"Episodios repetidos de abstinencia → mayor severidad progresiva","guid":"kGrbIOB_QLmM3ueVE4hOJg","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"29","text":"Explica por qué el AM con múltiples detoxes previos tiene ALTO riesgo de DT","guid":"JXBjvRdUTKKIRmJoo04fuQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"32","parent":"18","text":"Peculiaridades del cerebro añoso","guid":"oQsRcBllR4OS1VFMGoKzNg","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"Reserva cognitiva disminuida → clínica atípica","guid":"uYufLhLFRPWM7suEYTM0fQ","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"32","text":"Atrofia cerebral → mayor riesgo HSD ante caídas","guid":"zTRU-EwOQfS4-3CyBKS0qA","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"32","text":"Alteración BHE → mayor neurotoxicidad","guid":"d8xGcr9_QKWqoiYuu7cbvw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"36","parent":"0","text":"Presentación Clínica","guid":"Jfxq5ez3Ru6j6x73ugjoLA","children":[{"id":"37","parent":"36","text":"Fases temporales clásicas","guid":"Zl-wtxLRSwamEJ2q6Va1MQ","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"Fase 1 SÍNTOMAS MENORES (6-12 h)","guid":"IvaDvXskQYOgvujkOihwlA","children":[{"id":"39","parent":"38","text":"Temblor fino, ansiedad, insomnio","guid":"HeK-Q4SeSXyMBVqjIyy14g","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"38","text":"Náuseas, anorexia","guid":"61IZZn7PR3u5K0EnyZ8sCw","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"38","text":"HTA leve, taquicardia, diaforesis","guid":"KAW6hm5bT7Kj1LdXv3xO1w","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"38","text":"Hiperreflexia","guid":"RgNRvdPhSrqj5CCGDR1kaQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"43","parent":"37","text":"Fase 2 ALUCINOSIS ALCOHÓLICA (12-24 h)","guid":"cvevBRcyR9ek8vKzn3RCmQ","children":[{"id":"44","parent":"43","text":"Alucinaciones visuales > auditivas > táctiles","guid":"_13dK0XNRkyKA3gKDejzog","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"43","text":"Sensorio CONSERVADO (diferencia con DT)","guid":"C70r0XJgT9upT5pMoNnMWg","children":[]}]},{"id":"46","parent":"37","text":"Fase 3 CONVULSIONES (24-48 h)","guid":"tCy6dwL9Q1mP3Uio2Nht1w","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"Tónico-clónicas generalizadas","guid":"LlB_fr7cTnW1-swAsB-YgA","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"46","text":"Generalmente autolimitadas (<5 min)","guid":"XXfKI4ctSy65E7ttt0CO-Q","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"46","text":"Si focal o estado epiléptico → buscar OTRA causa (HSD, ACV)","guid":"B-fTHokbR86fbYFr99-Xag","children":[]}]},{"id":"50","parent":"37","text":"Fase 4 DELIRIUM TREMENS (48-96 h, hasta 7-10 días)","guid":"XIPuqEYbSmexgmfsGhnrdw","children":[{"id":"51","parent":"50","text":"Delirium + hiperactividad autonómica severa","guid":"_ivGJvgVRGmM2QJUETRBnQ","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"50","text":"Fiebre, taquicardia, HTA, diaforesis profusa","guid":"j9RNPSxxQPOUYUfxRiXIfQ","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"50","text":"Alucinaciones + desorientación + agitación","guid":"ONIxLRLGQLSg-WaLhaiFog","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"50","text":"Mortalidad ~1-4% (histórica 15%) → EN AM hasta 2-5x mayor","guid":"pwqOJykfQPupv_AprbKugQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"55","parent":"36","text":"Particularidades en el AM","guid":"42esA5jbTzO501XtooOFtw","children":[{"id":"56","parent":"55","text":"Inicio MÁS TARDÍO → puede debutar a las 72-96h del cese","guid":"j1thmQDeRy2MAztDUYXAEQ","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"55","text":"Duración PROLONGADA (hasta 2 semanas)","guid":"tqWe7K7SRWGq_uygF1hK2A","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"55","text":"Confusión como síntoma INAUGURAL → se confunde con delirium de otra causa","guid":"D5EgQAlFRtq3-M0PGE37NQ","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"55","text":"Menor expresión autonómica → puede tener CIWA bajo y estar grave","guid":"0TpLRxS9T2yAKJ8NzpdR0w","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"55","text":"SUBDIAGNOSTICADO → sospechar en todo delirium de causa no clara","guid":"Dxh4KWcjTg-fynz5YEl32w","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"61","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico Diferencial","guid":"OhCLoEx3TLK6pqFfbjZ7vw","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"Delirium por OTRA causa","guid":"kKMCw5VzTjCOj34fXyEy5g","children":[{"id":"63","parent":"62","text":"Sepsis / ITU / neumonía","guid":"7OpU8ku4QjOVOsBXT-FJlg","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"62","text":"Encefalopatía hepática (hiperamonemia, asterixis)","guid":"FeSwfs4ASFi7-qL7do9Jgg","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"62","text":"Hipo/hiperglicemia","guid":"CLAlx1YCRquacLx6h-Qx5w","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"62","text":"Hiponatremia (SIADH, diuréticos)","guid":"_-6PSjkuTUONz_XKWrT7uA","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"62","text":"Hipoxemia","guid":"lmLD-fNeTR-nHpGPVK9HjA","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"62","text":"Retención urinaria / fecal","guid":"L74q9IHbQUiiiWVZT7wXvA","children":[]}]},{"id":"69","parent":"61","text":"Causas neurológicas","guid":"jVotw0M4R56NxSMzE4iclQ","children":[{"id":"70","parent":"69","text":"Hematoma subdural (caída reciente → SIEMPRE TC cerebro)","guid":"egQnJuFlRCWSwim7VbOsLw","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"69","text":"ACV isquémico/hemorrágico","guid":"RymjgEj6R_am6Oxlq0DdBw","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"69","text":"Encefalitis / meningitis","guid":"Xp16kTUVQOawUo2NFkqc_w","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"69","text":"Estado postictal","guid":"LPxWgbDOQpmhrh90yfh5cg","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"69","text":"Encefalopatía de Wernicke","guid":"j1o0TgfdRxW_7C-aUWkCag","children":[]}]},{"id":"75","parent":"61","text":"Tóxico-metabólicas","guid":"fYPOJa87SC6BPzhGi5BEzg","children":[{"id":"76","parent":"75","text":"Intoxicación por BZD, opioides","guid":"9K2bjMaiQKa4-i5i3HLbhA","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"75","text":"Sd anticolinérgico (antihistamínicos, antimuscarínicos)","guid":"Y1WoBdttRDaI2Wt3o9pCoQ","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"75","text":"Síndrome serotoninérgico","guid":"vCK3hlEXSE2sU-kVh7OFFw","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"75","text":"Encefalopatía urémica","guid":"cGtfUGEvS_C3cvuJakbCGA","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"75","text":"Cetoacidosis alcohólica","guid":"Ryg1Ys2FRPCSR8mlJ2lQ6w","children":[]}]},{"id":"81","parent":"61","text":"Psiquiátricas","guid":"cQ6lzX1WT_ioxAZ9Pl0q7Q","children":[{"id":"82","parent":"81","text":"Psicosis aguda","guid":"1-lBLWJKQVmOp6kr3YoEMw","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"81","text":"Trastorno bipolar manía","guid":"2HrAMe8QRH62xQze2OF9Jw","children":[]},{"id":"84"